title: Lovely Bright Studio Apartment In Amazing Location!!
posting_body: ['Welcome to Assembly', "Built on the foundations of Oakland's historic auto row, there's more than tradition at work here; there's artistry and care built into every detail.", 'Studio to three-bedroom homes are beautifully crafted to fit your lifestyle with quartz counter tops, stainless-steel appliances, floor-to-ceiling windows, and wide plank flooring throughout.', 'Rich with thoughtfully-designed gathering spaces, including an expansive roof terrace, a two-level exercise haven and a peaceful courtyard, community is at the heart of Assembly.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Keyless entry', 'Floor to ceiling windows & wide plank flooring throughout', 'Yoga deck leading out to courtyard', 'Indoor-outdoor club room', 'In-home washer & dryer', 'Roof deck with gas grills & spacious cabanas', 'GE stainless steel appliance suite with gas stove top', 'Two-level fitness center with HIIT equipment & top of the line cardio machines', 'Nest thermostats with A/C', 'Glass door showers or shower & soaking tub duo', 'Courtyard with custom mural & fire pit', 'Quartz countertops & ceramic tile backsplash', 'Apt#322', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Check out the virtual tour: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
